# Debug / QA capture evidence is never committed — it goes to the Paperclip
# issue instead (see EVIDENCE-POLICY.md, JEL-141). Keep local harness output
# untracked so a run can't accidentally re-add it. CI also enforces this via
# tooling/ci/check-no-debug-evidence.sh.
results-*.md
*-capture.md
*-ondevice-*.md
*ntfy-raw*
*.jsonl
*.png
*.jpg
*.jpeg
*.sha256
last-run.*
*-payloads.json
capture-*.json
